Sorry to jump in here, but I&#39;ve experienced this on a few occasions.  The first time was when they came through on my iPod.  I always listen to instrumental meditation music when I go to bed as it tends to help me sleep better.  One night, I kept waking up to voices talking.  I still had the earphones in and the music was playing.  I kept hearing my name and then they would try to talk to me.  I finally had to tell them to stop cause it was getting very late and I had to be up for work in the morning.  They haven&#39;t come through the iPod since, but I will hear them every now and then before I go to bed.

Jeremy

----- Original Message ----
From: Michael Edwards &lt;f1cracker75@...&gt;
To: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com
Sent: Friday, April 11, 2008 9:43:06 PM
Subject: Re: [EVP-ITC] New file uploaded to EVP-ITC


That is funnny.. Yeah, I am amazed they can see us, and to think even before I got involved in Box EVP, I never thought once that they are right here in the room with us.

  Have a question for you. Margaret had mentioned in one of her posts that once we start Box Research, if we never have before, we are more likely to become chairaudient.

  Last night, was amazing for me while lying in bed. I heard them talking to me for the first time. It was really neat.

  Has this happened to you yet, or even to Kristin since the three of us are relatively new at this?



Rhonda W &lt;rhondak1973@ yahoo.com&gt; wrote:
        Heard what sounded like &quot;dude whatcha make that from?&quot; and the &quot;carving&quot;
  cool that they can see us...makes me not want to walk around nekkid any more haha

  Rhonda


